Pest problems in Srinagar homes and offices often increase during warmer and wetter months. Early treatment prevents infestations from spreading to kitchens, storage areas, and wiring.

## Common pest issues in Srinagar

- **Cockroaches and ants** in kitchens
- **Rodents** in older buildings and storage rooms
- **Termites** in wooden furniture and structures
- **Bed bugs** after travel or shared accommodation

## When to book pest control

- At the first sign of recurring pests — not after months of damage
- Before monsoon season for preventive treatment
- When moving into a new flat or office
- For restaurants and food businesses — regular scheduled visits

## Is treatment safe?

Licensed providers use approved products. Tell us if you have **children, pets, or food preparation areas** when booking so the technician can advise on ventilation and re-entry time.

